Movie Genre Impact on Crime â€“ Data Analysis Project

This project analyzes how different movie genres may correlate with crime trends over multiple years. Using datasets of movie genres and crime statistics, the project includes:

Year-wise crime comparison with genre popularity

Visual graphs showing potential trends

Heatmaps to identify correlations

Insights about whether certain genres show higher association with crime patterns

The goal of the analysis is to explore if movie content has any observable influence on real-world crime, using data visualization and statistical techniques.
